|      12 | OARS_TC_12   | **Security & input validation (SQL/XSS) and session timeout**<br>Steps: 1. Try SQL injection in username field (`' OR '1'='1`) 2. Try script tags in inputs `<script>alert(1)</script>` 3. Log in and remain idle until session timeout 4. Attempt action after timeout | Malicious strings as input; idle period (e.g., configured timeout 15 mins)            | Inputs are sanitized/escaped; login does not succeed for injection attempts; no script execution on UI; after timeout user is logged out and redirect to login when performing action |               |             |

